After what seems like a long time, Skeem Saam viewers caught a glimpse of principal Thobakgale's daughter, Lizzy, and they couldn't believe she was no longer on a wheelchair. Lizzy is back on her feet and a practising doctor - talk about surprises! There was a time when all viewers saw on Skeem Saam was Mangaliso, Lelo and a temporarily disabled Lizzy navigating their love triangle and then they disappeared only for Lizzy to return without warning. Twitter couldn't believe their eyes and had the memes to show it: